Description: This package empowers users to perform 3D GIS operations and advanced 3D network analyses—bringing the power of 3D modelling into open-source environments. This package supports (1) 3D geometry operations; (2) automated/convenient 3D path cost calculation; (3) Slope and direction-aware 3D routing; (4) Supports user-friendly, comprehensive 3D accessibility analysis.
